Sizi...!

00:12:06.390 --> 00:12:09.140
Peki, şimdi kim gelecek?

00:12:09.350 --> 00:12:10.730
Ben!

00:12:10.930 --> 00:12:13.270
Tenshinhan, dikkat et!

00:12:31.370 --> 00:12:34.580
